title: error on startup after new patch. help!!

embed.description: Imgur: The most awesome images on the Internet.

body: get this message when i try to start up league. anyone else with a fix?

replies.body: i got the same problem. happened to me after i restarted my computer after lol update
Hey, did you find a solution to the problem?
That's a strange window to appear.  Is this happening on the updated client?  Are you using any third party programs that interact with the client?
no add ons at all. when i first updated the client it worked. but once i closed league and restarted it this showed up. i can't even get to the login screen.
